About the property

28 Grovedale Circuit is a house in Cairnlea. It sits on a 648m lot. The property has a $1,177,000 estimated value. It is located within Brimbank council, with no bushfire, flood, or heritage overlays detected. It is zoned for Cairnlea Park Primary School, Victoria University Secondary College-Cairnlea Campus, and 2 other schools. It has reliable NBN Fibre to the Node and 5G mobile coverage.
